text: Lidingö SK is a sports club in Lidingö in Sweden. The men's volleyball team won the Swedish national championshis 18 times between 1966 and 1981. The team then won again in 1987 and 1990. The men's junior volleyball team won the Swedish national championship for four times in a row between 1975 and 1978. ==References== ==Other websites== *Lidingös SK *Lidingös SK handboll *Lidingös SK Volleyboll Category:1933 establishments in Europe Category:Handball clubs in Sweden Category:Volleyball clubs in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:1930s establishments in Sweden
